LINE.Text: We live in the age of TMBI
Meandering meetings. excessive emails and unclear
conversations are wasting our time and getting in the way of work.
Poor communication doesn't just waste time, it creates a lack of
clarity and leads to poor execution across the entire organization.
The most innovative Fortune 500 companies are embracing lean
communication to reclaim precious time and productivity.
To learn how Fortune 500 companies and elite military units are
embracing lean communication visit www.the lab.com
